/* eslint-disable react/prop-types */
/* eslint-disable react/jsx-props-no-spreading */
import dynamic from 'next/dynamic';
import {useForm} from 'useforms'
import { CopyBlock, dracula } from 'react-code-blocks'
import { Row, Col } from 'react-grid-system';
import { Box, Input, Stack, Button, ButtonGroup, Checkbox, Radio, FormControl, FormLabel } from "@chakra-ui/core";

const ReactJson=dynamic(import ('react-json-view'),{ssr:false});
const Docs=dynamic(import ('./index.mdx'),{ssr:false});


const initialValues = {
   name:"Jesse",
   email:"jesse@jesse.com",
   pets:["felix"],
   others:{
     radio:null
   }
}

export default function GetStartForm(){

   const [{values, reset},{input}] = useForm({onChange:true, initialValues})
   const codeBlock = `
  import {useForm} from 'useforms'

  const initialValues = {
      name:"Jesse",
      email:"jesse@jesse.com",
      pets:["felix"]
  }

  function ControlledForm(){

      const [{values, reset},{input}] = useForm({onChange:true, initialValues})
      return (
        <>
            <input {...input("email", "email")}/>
                    /* or  */
            <input {...input({name:"email", type:"email", required:true})}/>

            <input {...input("name" ,"name")}/>            
            <input {...input("pets.0" ,"text")}/>
            <input {...input("pets.1" ,"text")}/>         
            <input {...input("accept", "checkCol")}/>
            <input value="1" {...input("others.radio", "radio")}/>First
            <input value="2" {...input("others.radio", "radio")}/>Second
            <input value="3" {...input("others.radio", "radio")}/>Third
        </>   
      )
  }
   `

   return (
     <Box marginTop={20}>
       <Row>
         <Col>
           <Docs />
         </Col>
       </Row>
       <Row>
         <Col lg={6}>
           <Box padding="5" borderWidth={1} borderRadius={4} marginTop={10}>
             <Stack spacing={3}>
               <Input placeholder="E-mail" size="lg" {...input({name:"email", type:"email", required:true})} />
               <Input placeholder="Name" size="lg" {...input("name" ,"text")} />
               <Input placeholder="Pets 0" size="lg" {...input("pets.0", "text")} />
               <Input placeholder="Pets 1" size="lg" {...input("pets.1", "text")} />
               <Checkbox {...input("accept", "checkbox")}>Checkbox</Checkbox>
             </Stack>

             <FormControl marginTop={5}>
               <FormLabel htmlFor="email">Radio</FormLabel>     
               <Stack spacing={3}>
                 <Radio value="1" {...input("others.radio", "radio")}>First</Radio>
                 <Radio value="2" {...input("others.radio", "radio")}>Second</Radio>
                 <Radio value="3" {...input("others.radio", "radio")}>Third</Radio>
               </Stack>
             </FormControl>

             <Stack spacing={3}>
               <ButtonGroup spacing={4} marginTop={5}>
                 <Button variantColor="teal" size="lg" onClick={reset}>
                   Reset
                 </Button>
                 <Button variantColor="teal" size="lg" onClick={()=>{}}>
                   Submit
                 </Button>
               </ButtonGroup>
             </Stack>
           </Box>
         </Col>
         <Col lg={6}>
           <Box marginTop={10}>
             <ReactJson src={values} name="values" theme="colors" style={{borderRadius:3, padding:15}} />
           </Box>
         </Col>
       </Row>
       <Row>
         <Col lg={12} id="code-block" style={{marginTop:50}}>
           <CopyBlock
             className="code-block"
             text={codeBlock}
             language="jsx"
             showLineNumbers
             theme={dracula}
             codeBlock
           />
         </Col>
       </Row>
     </Box>
   )
}
